br />\n依家有薩德，開戰既幾會細左好多<br />\n<br />\n加上依家大陸入面既反薩德既示威已經消失哂，反美變左要靠美國了。</blockquote><br />\n北泡技術應該飛到支那境内就爆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n北泡無支那支持亡國九世。 佢地D核武開發實驗室全部支那俾錢。技術轉讓應該無。"},{"pid":"b78937906fae6b8d0274891e915e73c0bc95cb3a","tid":222332,"uid":28195,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-29T16:38:12.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>cctvb好似好耐無出國外採訪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n最多係去支那或者台灣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n國外新聞全部用人地片<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n好多比呢單新聞有意義同對香港有影響都冇專登派記者搭飛機採訪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\nCCTVB每日重點新聞<br />\n<br />\n1. 中國外交部聲明，多項<br />\n2. 美國槍擊案，詳細報導<br />\n3. 如果無2. .就報ISIS在歐洲既恐襲，全世界都好危險<br />\n4. 再有中央高層官員因貪被捕（潛意：中央再次自我完善，成為最完美政府）<br />\n<br />\n港聞<br />\n1. 泛民拉布，建造業無工開<br />\n2. 又有泛民人仕犯罪，被律政司起訴，被捕<br />\n4. 黎緊母親節，唔係講老母，係講花幾多錢，茶樓生意如何，晚飯酒席同舊年比，有無貴到"},{"pid":"1aeb07b76f7fd7c440a55097646000fbd54b91a2","tid":222332,"uid":55533,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-29T16:40:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eb9f72a6dd80bf26153de2b4a5cdbd6c0a73dd3c","tid":222332,"uid":28195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-29T16:41:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>執撚左佢啦CCTVB 正常後生果班已經無人睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n後生果班睇無線就好肯定唔多正常"},{"pid":"f4dd2b338e364474cbf567c58d89bb7edcfc6e02","tid":222332,"uid":9732,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-29T16:42:40.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>cctvb好似好耐無出國外採訪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n最多係去支那或者台灣<img src=\"/ass